  "title": "The Age of Fable",
  "description": "Drawing on the works of Homer, Ovid, Virgil, and other classical authors, as well as an immense trove of stories about the Norse gods and heroes, The Age of Fable offers lively retellings of the myths of the Greek and Roman gods: Venus and Adonis, Jupiter and Juno, Daphne and Apollo, and many others. [Source][1].\r\n\r\n\r\n  [1]: http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/0486411079/ref=pd_lpo_sbs_dp_ss_2?pf_rd_p=1944687582&pf_rd_s=lpo-top-stripe-1&pf_rd_t=201&pf_rd_i=0452011523&pf_rd_m=ATVPDKIKX0DER&pf_rd_r=0HP4FXC8G5H55E0BK1WV",
